  "body": "***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: Follow up to #4754. Some Dapps has a pop-ups / modal windows prior to requesting a contact to 'Sign message or Sign Transaction as a confirmation of account. We fail to \"notify\" the modal window about the cancellation of the transaction when pressing Android device 'Back' button so it is not possible to re-Sign once again in Dapp: e.g. CryptoKitties, Airswap affected \r\n\r\nNote: it's all fine using `X` close top-left button from `Sign message`/ `Sign Transaction` screens.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nUser can proceed to Sign transaction/Sign message screen\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior**\r\nUser can't proceed to Sign transaction/Sign message screen. \r\nCryptoKitties persist to display 'Signing In...' button in 'Create account' pop-up.\r\nAirswap persist to display `Connect with Status. Sign to confirm your account` screen\r\n\r\n### Reproduction (with Airswap)\r\n\r\n- Open Status and create an account (re-login under Mainnet if you are not on this network)\r\n- Navigate to `Open Dapp` -> `Airswap` -> `Open`\r\n- `Start trading` -> tap any token (e.g. `ADT`)\r\n- Tap 'Sign in using Status`\r\n- Press Android 'Back' button on the `Sign transaction` screen\r\n\r\n### Reproduction (with CryptoKitties)\r\n- Open Status and create an account (re-login under Mainnet if you are not on this network)\r\n- Navigate to `Open Dapp` -> `CryptoKitties` -> `Open`\r\n- `Start Meow` -> Enter valid email value and tap `Continue`\r\n- Check all checkmarks to proceed and tap `Sign Up`\r\n- Press Android 'Back' button on the `Sign message` screen\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop nightly 19th of June (0.9.20 (6074)\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF session for Cryptokitties: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8497869/sessions/4394296271/?accessToken=jTMHF-2yBK1Qg6bq5RevpCRtDTs",
